{"tid":350120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件自己最柒既事","createTime":"2017-08-07T04:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T04:25:18.000Z","uid":131430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe80b23b2563e7c8f75d4040b715f3f3b84a2b05","tid":350120,"uid":131430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n有次同屋企人 老人家 姨媽姑姐叔父 表兄弟姐妹 食飯<br />\n食食下我拎電話出黎㩒<br />\n突然間有人拍我背脊<br />\n後面枱成枱人望住我，有個 Waiter 企係我身邊<br />\nWaiter: 先生，你跌左野 (指一指地下)<br />\n果陣其實好靜，全部人靜哂<br />\n我望一望地下<br />\n仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去完條女屋企唔記得左擺返低個 Dom ，跌左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一腳踢左個 Dom 去唔知邊度 跟住話：唔係我個喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成家人問咩事咩事 勁老尷"}]}